(759, 83, '_yoast_wpseo_metadesc', 'The National Irish Canadian Cultural Centre was established to advance Irish culture in all its forms in Canada. It this through community building events such as monthly pancake breakfasts, a St. Brigid’s Day concert in February, St. Patrick’s Day events in March, Bloomsday celebration on 16 June, a Fall festival in September and many others.'),
