nce.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir="ltr">[View Plan –pdf link]</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2 dir="ltr">The Kildare Room</h2>\r\n<p dir="ltr">The Kildare Room is located in the basement space of Saint Brigid’s Centre. This room features newly repointed original stone walls, beautifully renovated washrooms, gallery lighting and most importantly, versatility. This space is exceptionally adaptable to different events and ideal for wedding receptions, banquets, private parties, small concerts and performances, and art exhibitions.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.714285714;">Capacity: 258 standing, 200 theatrical seating, 170 banquet seating</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.714285714;">Located in the basement of Saint Brigid’s – entrance is located on Cumberland Street.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.714285714;">Approximately 50’ x 50’</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.714285714;">16’ x16’ stage</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.714285714;">Stage lighting: 8 spotlights in front, 8 LEDs at the back, with lighting board, plus house lights</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.714285714;">Gallery lighting along side walls</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.714285714;">Projector screen installed on stage</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.714285714;">Basic 4-channel P/A system available</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.714285714;">5 individual unisex washroom units</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.714285714;">Tables, chairs, podium available.</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.714285714;">Bar services available</span></li>\r\n	<li><span style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.714285714;">This space is not accessible by wheelchair</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p dir="ltr">[View Plan – pdf link]</p>\r\n&nbsp;', 'Venue Rental', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '44-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-08-09 01:59:41', '2013-08-09 01:59:41', '', 44, 'http://saintbrigidscentre.com/44-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
