r services available</span></li>\n	<li><span style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.714285714;">This space is not accessible by wheelchair</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p dir="ltr"><a href="http://saintbrigidscentre.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Kildare-Room-Floor-Plan-dimensioned.pdf" target="_blank">View Kildare Room Floor Plan [pdf]</a></p>\n&nbsp;', 'Venue Rental', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '44-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-07-27 17:09:58', '2014-07-27 17:09:58', '', 44, 'http://saintbrigidscentre.com/44-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
