(283, 2, '2014-07-29 18:25:00', '2014-07-29 18:25:00', '<a href="http://saintbrigidscentre.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Jessestewart_Aug1.jpg"><img src="http://saintbrigidscentre.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Jessestewart_Aug1-500x300.jpg" alt="Jessestewart" width="500" height="300" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-273" /></a>\n\nAward-winning percussionist and composer Jesse Stewart presents a multimedia project of interstellar proportions: the contemporary remix of images and sounds recorded on two golden records affixed to the Voyager spacecraft.\n“The launching of this ‘bottle’ into the cosmic ‘ocean’ says something very hopeful about life on this planet.” – Carl Sagan.\n\nDATE: 01/08/2014 @ 22:00 – 23:30\nPRICE/PRIX $30 General Admission\nCONTACT: 613-234-6306   E-mail\n', 'Sounds from Space: The Voyager Golden Record Remix Project', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'sounds-from-space-the-voyager-golden-record-remix-project', '', '', '2014-08-05 14:53:21', '2014-08-05 14:53:21', '', 0, 'http://saintbrigidscentre.com/?page_id=283', 0, 'page', '', 0),
